    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? This car is an absolute dream and has been my pride and joy! It\u2019s in flawless condition\u2014I\u2019ve kept it garaged, strictly smoke-free, and I\u2019ve waxed it more times than I can count. It looks and drives like it just left the dealership. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm ready to pass it on to someone who will appreciate a truly perfect vehicle. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
