      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen exhibits flawless mechanical health, with a recent valve adjustment and a preemptively reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag 420G manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, transmitting power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable Differential Lock. The suspension maintains its original geometry with zero bushing deflection, providing the communicative steering feedback these chassis are renowned for. Finished in Titanium Silver with a pristine interior, this car retains all factory VIN tags and shows no signs of thermal fatigue or fluid seepage in the engine bay. A truly turn-key enthusiast piece with a linear torque curve and an exhilarating 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
