    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' find, preserved in showroom-fresh condition. The exterior features a mirror-like finish with deep gloss, completely free of rock chips, swirls, or parking lot dings. It has been treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating to maintain its luster. The factory alloy wheels are immaculate, showing zero curb rash, and are fitted with high-performance tires. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, with no bolster wear or creasing. The dashboard and interior trim are flawless, showing no UV fading or scratches. Every feature, from the high-fidelity audio system to the climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is perfect. It has been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. We have a complete, organized binder of every service record since new, along with all original keys, manuals, and the window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a pristine example that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
